    # Based on Sample 9
    "i think this because you do {num1}/{den1} * {factor1} = {adj_num1}/{common_den}, then {num2}/{den2} * {factor2} = {adj_num2}/{common_den}, then {adj_num1}/{common_den} + {adj_num2}/{common_den} = {correct_num}/{common_den}.",
