            f"{frac_denom} into {total} is {one_part} then times {frac_num} is {correct_answer} so {total} take away {correct_answer} is {wrong_answer}.",
            f"I divided {total} by {frac_denom} to get a {frac_denom}th then multiplied it by {complement_num}",
