        f"i think this because as all probabilities add up to 1, 1 - {probability} is {1 - probability}.",
        f"i think that this is because it is a low value but not impossible.",
        f"it's a very low chance ({probability}) so it's less likely.",
        f"because it is {description_str} so it is closer to 0",
